# Responsive Landing Page

This project is a simple landing page template designed to showcase CSS animations and responsiveness using media queries.

## Features

- Utilizes semantic HTML5 elements for a clear and logical layout.
- Implements CSS animations to enhance the user experience.
- Designs that adapt seamlessly to various screen sizes using media queries.
- Provides a well-commented CSS code explaining the purpose of each rule and animation.
- Includes a README file documenting design choices and how to view the project.
responsive-landing-page/
│
├── index.html
├── styles.css
└── README.md

## Getting Started

To view the project, simply download or clone the repository to your local machine and open the `index.html` file in your web browser and clone it.


